{{Vgname|上古卷轴V：天际·炉火|en=The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim – Hearthfire}}是《[[上古卷轴V：天际|上古卷轴V：天际]]》的第二个官方[[追加下载内容|追加下载内容]]（DLC）。游戏由[[贝塞斯达游戏工作室|贝塞斯达游戏工作室]]开发设计和[[贝塞斯达软件公司|贝塞斯达软件公司]]发行。游戏于2012年9月4日在微软的[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台首发。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bethblog.com/2012/08/28/hearthfire-coming-to-xbox-live-on-september-4th/ |title=Hearthfire – Coming to Xbox LIVE on September 4th (Updated) | Bethesda Blog |publisher=Bethblog.com |language=en |date=2012-08-28 |accessdate=2014-12-27 |archive-date=2012-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120830094323/http://www.bethblog.com/2012/08/28/hearthfire-coming-to-xbox-live-on-september-4th/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>接着[[Microsoft_Windows|Windows]]版于2012年10月5日发行了。<ref>[http://www.bethblog.com/2012/10/04/hearthfire-available-on-steam/ Hearthfire available on Steam | Bethesda Blog<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bethblog.com/2012/10/04/hearthfire-available-on-steam/ |date=20180701165022 }}{{en}}</ref>最后[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]版分别于2013年2月12日和13日在北美和欧洲发行。<ref name="GameRant">{{cite web|url=http://gamerant.com/skyrim-dlc-ps3-february-release/|title='Skyrim's' 'Dragonborn,' 'Hearthfire' & 'Dawnguard' Finally Confirmed for February PS3 Release|work=GameRant.com|last=Sipple|first=Brian|language=en|date=2013-01-18|accessdate=2014-12-27|archive-date=2019-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806122815/https://gamerant.com/skyrim-dlc-ps3-february-release/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/games/Skyrim-Hearthfire-Releasing-PS3-Today-52729.html|title=Skyrim Hearthfire Releasing On PS3 Today|language=en|accessdate=2014-12-27|date=2013-02-19|archive-date=2013-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130222045621/http://www.cinemablend.com/games/Skyrim-Hearthfire-Releasing-PS3-Today-52729.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latinospost.com/articles/12372/20130218/ps3-skyrim-dlc-release-date-hearthfire-releases.htm|title=PS3 Skyrim DLC Release Date: Hearthfire Releases Tomorrow, Feb. 19, Followed By Dawnguard One Week Later|language=en|accessdate=2014-12-27|date=2013-02-18|archive-date=2013-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130220184736/http://www.latinospost.com/articles/12372/20130218/ps3-skyrim-dlc-release-date-hearthfire-releases.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在《炉火》里，玩家将被能够打造属于自己的家庭，如添加家庭成员以及抚养孩子成长。玩家也能建造一些独立的房屋，如诊疗所、图书馆、炼丹室、马车库等。除此之外，玩家也可以选择体验园艺，还有聘请管家来帮忙管理家务。

